{"tid":757582,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(前途盡毀) 與13歲女互換私處照逼口交　22歲準機師囚21月","createTime":"2018-07-27T03:37:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-27T09:18:09.000Z","uid":54337,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"45e201629f22cc8b048bdf50e8898a6623cf9775","tid":757582,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T03:37:37.000Z","msg":"與13歲女互換私處照逼口交　22歲準機師囚21月<br />\n<br />\n以成為飛機師為目標的22歲男生，赴澳洲修讀相關課程前，去年11月在社交網站向新相識的13歲女童提出濕吻及口交的要求，女童雖拒絕，但同意互相交換私處照片。男生取得女童私處照後就拿來要挾她，還傳給她兩名同學，被女童家人及時揭發。被告林天朗早前承認一項刑事恐嚇及兩項發布兒童色情物品罪，今(27日)在區域法院被判囚21個月。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n法官判刑時，引述報告指被告沒有精神問題，願意接受心理醫生的建議，報告亦指被告雖然後悔，但對於造成事件的因素卻認知不足，重犯程度屬於中等。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n法官指被告沒有案底及年輕，惟他先以威嚇方式，令女童交出照片，再圖迫令女童與他做一些性行為，更向女童的兩名未成年男女同學發布女童的照片，案件嚴重。法庭亦需考慮到媒體容易被成年人濫用來傷害年幼兒童的情況，故須判以阻嚇刑罰。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180727/mobile/bkn-20180727105601339-0727_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180727%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20180727105601339-0727_00822_001.html&d=rPk%2BqPz8NcK6ymllK2Cm5U%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=e603c2e9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180727/mobile/bkn-20180727105601339-0727_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"87507b87da4272b1fdf07996130403f43a143943","tid":757582,"uid":39800,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T03:39:56.000Z","msg":"連相關課程都未開始讀咁都叫準機師？"},{"pid":"75a0a4856e3ec1ec06819da9e8d82f2b02e22ad3","tid":757582,"uid":511,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"87507b87da4272b1fdf07996130403f43a143943","tid":757582,"uid":39800,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T03:39:56.000Z","msg":"連相關課程都未開始讀咁都叫準機師？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T03:40:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcf0b91f495a8621f0a55ad09174a6d9c9c11ecd","tid":757582,"uid":54337,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T03:43:34.000Z","msg":"毒撚未拍拖，未結婚，但想結婚，係咪可以自稱準新郎哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n傳媒用字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"987f617b57ce66344751dbe4afa831755eb66966","tid":757582,"uid":6799,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"75a0a4856e3ec1ec06819da9e8d82f2b02e22ad3","tid":757582,"uid":511,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"87507b87da4272b1fdf07996130403f43a143943","tid":757582,"uid":39800,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T03:39:56.000Z","msg":"連相關課程都未開始讀咁都叫準機師？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T03:40:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T03:43:48.000Z","msg":"大家都可以係準律師 準醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96f5324381a15803207a32feef6f4743ee945e32","tid":757582,"uid":92603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T03:44:55.000Z","msg":"其實佢讀左咩課程？"},{"pid":"d3d06a53b9cb5588cbe5594ebe7121173bc6ea00","tid":757582,"uid":156376,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"96f5324381a15803207a32feef6f4743ee945e32","tid":757582,"uid":92603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T03:44:55.000Z","msg":"其實佢讀左咩課程？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T03:47:12.000Z","msg":"赴澳洲修讀相關課程<span style=\"color: red;\">前</span>"},{"pid":"0a2f1d044b24f9a06b9156031c0f1f5b6a856cd0","tid":757582,"uid":62384,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T03:47:22.000Z","msg":"夢想係機師就係準機師？"},{"pid":"134dbdf9b2a453c860b4146435d8e769754421b6","tid":757582,"uid":28181,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T03:49:56.000Z","msg":"都未讀就想教人「渣」係隻「飛機」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\"